<div class="nav subnav d-flex spacer-top-20 spacer-bottom-20"><div class="subnav-span-left d-flex align-left"><figure class="spacer-right-30"><a href="/ct/2020/april/" title=""><img src="https://www-images.christianitytoday.com/images/115969.png?w=225" srcset="https://www-images.christianitytoday.com/images/115969.png?w=450 2x" width="225" alt="April" title="April" /></a></figure><div class="o-hidden"><h3 class="themeCollection-sm"><a class="themeCollection-sm" href="/ct/2020/april/">April 2020</a></h3><div class="short-desc spacer-top-15 spacer-bottom-50"><span>Digital editions:*</span><div class="spacer-top-3"><span><a class="color-red js-login js-clickTrack tooltip" data-category="Article" data-action="TopNav Magazine" data-label="Reader Friendly PDF" alt="You must be a subscriber to use this feature. Please log in or subscribe now." title="You must be a subscriber to use this feature. Please log in or subscribe now.">Reader Friendly PDF</a></span><span class="seprator">|</span><span><a class="color-red js-login js-clickTrack tooltip" data-category="Article" data-action="TopNav Magazine" data-label="Standard PDF" alt="You must be a subscriber to use this feature. Please log in or subscribe now." title="You must be a subscriber to use this feature. Please log in or subscribe now.">Standard PDF</a></span></div>
